---
import { Anchor } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="about-section" class="py-24 bg-neutral-50 relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center text-center border-t-4 border-black">
  <!-- Background Decor -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-10 bg-grid-pattern"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="mb-12 flex justify-center">
         <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-accent border-4 border-black shadow-brutal flex items-center justify-center rotate-3 transform hover:rotate-6 hover:scale-110 transition-all">
            <Anchor className="w-10 h-10 text-black -rotate-3" />
         </div>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-black mb-8 leading-tight uppercase transform -rotate-1">
        BİZ <span class="bg-primary px-4 border-4 border-black inline-block shadow-brutal transform rotate-2">KİMİZ?</span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-black font-bold leading-relaxed mb-16 relative">
        <span class="absolute -top-8 -left-8 text-8xl text-secondary/20 font-black">"</span>
        Düşünce ve Kitap Topluluğu, entelektüel üretimin tüketimden daha değerli olduğuna inananların limanıdır. 
        Amacımız, fikirlerin çarpıştığı ama asla incitmediği, derinliğin sığlığa galip geldiği bir alan yaratmaktır.
        <span class="absolute -bottom-16 -right-8 text-8xl text-secondary/20 font-black">"</span>
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 pt-12">
          <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 shadow-brutal hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-1 hover:translate-y-1 transition-all">
             <span class="block text-4xl font-black text-black mb-2">5K+</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-bold text-black uppercase bg-accent inline-block px-1">Aktif Üye</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 shadow-brutal hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-1 hover:translate-y-1 transition-all">
             <span class="block text-4xl font-black text-black mb-2">120+</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-bold text-black uppercase bg-primary inline-block px-1">Atölye</span>
          </div>
           <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 shadow-brutal hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-1 hover:translate-y-1 transition-all">
             <span class="block text-4xl font-black text-black mb-2">850+</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-bold text-black uppercase bg-secondary text-white inline-block px-1">Analiz</span>
          </div>
           <div class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-4 shadow-brutal hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-1 hover:translate-y-1 transition-all">
             <span class="block text-4xl font-black text-black mb-2">∞</span>
             <span class="text-sm font-bold text-black uppercase bg-black text-white inline-block px-1">Fikir</span>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</section>
